WHEN it seemed to him time to march up into the coun­ try, he made it his pretext for doing so that be wished to expel the Pisidians entirely from the territory, and mustered, as if for the purpose of attacking them, the whole of the troops, as well Barbarian as Greek, that were on the spot.
