The officers communicated these orders to their soldiers ;
and, when the trumpeter gave the signal, they presented arms and advanced.
Then, as they proceeded with a quicker pace and loud shouts, the soldiers of their own ac­ cord took to running, bearing down upon the tents of the Per­ sians.
