Next came forward a Mysian, with a light shield in each hand, and danced, sometimes acting as if two adversaries were attacking him ;
sometimes he used his shields as if en­ gaged with only one ;
sometimes he whirled about, and threw a summerset, still keeping the shields in his hands, presenting an interesting spectacle.
